Label: LABEL
Measurand: C ('has specified input' some %) and (realizes some ('analyte role' and ('inheres in' some %)))
Measurement Units: C 'has specified output' some ('has measurement unit label' value '%')

Label: creatine kinase activity assay
Description: An activity assay that measures the activity of creatine kinase in a sample.

Label: creatinine concentration assay
Description: An analyte assay that measures the concentration of creatinine in a sample.

Label: urea nitrogen concentration assay
Description: An analyte assay that measures the concentration of urea nitrogen in a sample.

Label: white blood cell count assay
Description: A hematology assay that measures the number of white blood cells in a volume of sample.

Label: mean cell volume assay
Description: A hematology assay that measures the average volume of a red blood cell in a sample, calculated by multiplying the volume of blood by the hematocrit and dividing that product by the number of red blood cells in that volume.

Label: alkaline phosphatase activity assay
Description: An activity assay that measures the activity of alkaline phosphatase in a sample.

Label: cholesterol concentration assay
Description: An analyte assay that measures the concentration of cholesterol in a sample.

Label: total protein concentration assay
Description: An analyte assay that measures the concentration of total protein in a sample.

Label: sorbitol dehydrogenase activity assay
Description: An activity assay that measures the activity of sorbitol dehydrogenase in a sample.

Label: triglyceride concentration assay
Description: An analyte assay that measures the concentration of triglyceride in a sample.

Label: basophil count assay
Description: A hematology assay that measures the number of basophil cells in a volume of sample.

Label: eosinophil count assay
Description: A hematology assay that measures the number of eosinophil cells in a volume of sample.

Label: erythrocyte count assay
Description: A hematology assay that measures the number of erythrocyte cells in a volume of sample.

Label: hemoglobin concentration assay
Description: A hematology assay that measures the concentration of hemoglobin in a sample.

Label: lymphocyte count assay
Description: A hematology assay that measures the number of lymphocyte cells in a volume of sample.

Label: monocyte count assay
Description: A hematology assay that measures the number of monocyte cells in a volume of sample.

Label: neutrophil count assay
Description: A hematology assay that measures the number of neutrophil cells in a volume of sample.

Label: platelet count assay
Description: A hematology assay that measures the number of platelet cells in a volume of sample.

Label: reticulocyte count assay
Description: A hematology assay that measures the number of reticulocyte cells in a volume of sample.

Label: mean cell hemoglobin assay
Description: A hematology assay that measures the amount of hemoglobin in an average red blood cell in a sample, calculated by dividing the average mass of hemoglobin by the number of red blood cells in a volume of blood.

Label: mean cell hemoglobin concentration assay
Description: A hematology assay that measures the concentration of hemoglobin in a given volume of packed red blood cells in a sample, calculated by dividing the average concentration of hemoglobin by the hematocrit.

Label: albumin concentration assay
Description: An analyte assay that measures the concentration of albumin in a sample.
